sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Data Scientist
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard
    participant DSP as data-science-pipelines-operator
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows
    participant DataPrep as Pipeline Step:<br/>Data Preparation
    participant TrainOp as training-operator
    participant TrainJob as PyTorchJob/TFJob
    participant S3 as S3 Storage
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry
    participant KServe as KServe

    User->>Dashboard: 1. Submit ML pipeline
    Dashboard->>DSP: 2. Create DSPA CR<br/>(pipeline definition)
    DSP->>Argo: 3. Create Argo Workflow

    Note over Argo,S3: Data Preparation
    Argo->>DataPrep: 4a. Execute data prep step
    DataPrep->>S3: 4b. Read raw data
    DataPrep->>S3: 4c. Write processed data

    Note over Argo,MLflow: Model Training
    Argo->>TrainOp: 5a. Create PyTorchJob/TFJob CR
    TrainOp->>TrainJob: 5b. Create distributed training pods
    TrainJob->>S3: 5c. Load training data
    TrainJob->>TrainJob: 5d. Distributed training
    TrainJob->>MLflow: 5e. Log metrics and artifacts
    TrainJob->>S3: 5f. Save model checkpoints

    Note over Argo,ModelReg: Model Registration
    Argo->>ModelReg: 6. Register trained model<br/>(version, lineage, metrics)

    Note over Argo,KServe: Model Deployment
    Argo->>KServe: 7a. Create InferenceService CR
    KServe->>S3: 7b. Load model artifacts
    KServe->>KServe: 7c. Deploy predictor pods

    Note over Argo,User: Pipeline Completion
    Argo->>Dashboard: 8a. Update pipeline status
    Dashboard->>User: 8b. Display completion<br/>(deployed model endpoint)
